

pc051

Version = C
Subversion = 209

This file describes PCB fabrication details of a board with eight 8-channel
14-bit 40MSample/s ADC + FPGA for SoLiD readout.
 
contact:	David.Cussans@bristol.ac.uk
		tel: 0117 95 46879
		     0117 33 17199
		fax: 0117 925 5624


Files produced by Cadence Allegro PE16.6

Artwork:
--------

Format: Gerber RS-274X , parameters described in art_param.txt. 
All layers viewed from top

