Fiducial Marks
--------------

1mm round copper marks at x=30mm , y = 10mm from lower left of board. Top and bottom

1mm round copper marks at x=30mm , y = 440mm from lower left of board. Top and bottom

1mm square copper marks at x=120mm , y = 10mm from lower left of board. Top and bottom

